<section ID="chapter.widgets.scrollframe">
  <TITLE>Scrollframe widget</title>
<p>
<picture.extern to="scrollframe.gif" type=gif>

<<<local
   Frame=td(label(text:"Label" width:10 height:10)
            button(text:"Hello" action:QTk.bell)
            button(text:"Close" action:toplevel#close))
   Desc=scrollframe(glue:nswe
                    Frame
                    tdscrollbar:true
                    lrscrollbar:true)
in
   {{QTk.build td(Desc)} show}
end
>>>


<subsection> <TITLE>Description</TITLE>

<P>
A scrollframe is a rectangular area that can display one widget. This widget can be bigger than the actual size of the scrollframe. Scrollbars can be added to the scrollframe to change the viewable area.
</P>

